        <h3 class="hard-news-unit__headline">
            <a href="/web/20150105211826/http://www.bbc.co.uk/persian/iran/2015/01/150105_l39_hollande_nuclear_iran" class="hard-news-unit__headline-link">
                رئیس جمهور فرانسه: در مورد برنامه هسته ای ایران کوتاه نمی‌آییم
            </a>
        </h3>

            <div class="hard-news-unit__image">
                    <div class="responsive-image responsive-image--16by9">
                            <img src="/web/20150105211826im_/http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/ws/200/amz/worldservice/live/assets/images/2015/01/05/150105091027_francois_hollande_640x360_afp_nocredit.jpg" class="responsive-image__image js-image-replace" alt="فرانسوا اولاند" width="640" height="360" />
                    </div>
            </div>

